import './landing.css'; import React from 'react'; import NavBar from '../navbar/navbar.js'; import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography'; /** * Changes the visibility of an element * * @param {*} action either show or hide * @param {*} id of the element to change visibility of */ function changeVisibility(action, id) { const element = document.getElementById(id); const expandedElement = document.getElementById(id + "Expanded"); console.log(element) switch (action) { case "show" : { element.style.visibility = "hidden"; expandedElement.style.visibility = "visible"; break; } case "hide" : { element.style.visibility = "visible"; expandedElement.style.visibility = "hidden"; break; } default : break; } }; function Landing() { return ( <>
AHMED KATARY Computer Scientist | Artist
{/** Group One **/}
{changeVisibility('show', 'projectResearch')}}>
Projects / Research
{changeVisibility('show', 'papersPublications')}}>
Papers / Publications
{changeVisibility('show', 'educationWork')}}>
Education / Work
{/** Group One Expanded **/}
{changeVisibility('hide', 'projectResearch')}}>
Projects / Research
{changeVisibility('hide', 'papersPublications')}}>
Papers / Publications
{changeVisibility('hide', 'educationWork')}}>
Education / Work
); } export default Landing;
